  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The Great Battle IV is the fourth entry in Banpresto's Compati Hero series for the Super Famicom. The game is a crossover action game title involving the characters from Kamen Rider, Ultraman, and Mobile Suit Gundam franchise respectively. Gameplay is similar to Mega Man X.",
